    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/b513da573c570651b41c9adb1e6f7d06.poster.avif?t=1771831372\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/b513da573c570651b41c9adb1e6f7d06.webm?t=1771831372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/b513da573c570651b41c9adb1e6f7d06.mp4?t=1771831372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简单的控制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过直观的控制，掌握《Blade Blitz》变得轻而易举。只需一个操纵杆和两个按钮即可开始切片和切块。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/a5ab2a7986915b71eca7cbf0b5bf7e93.poster.avif?t=1771831372\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/a5ab2a7986915b71eca7cbf0b5bf7e93.webm?t=1771831372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/a5ab2a7986915b71eca7cbf0b5bf7e93.mp4?t=1771831372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>阿里纳斯</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在四个独特的竞技场中一决高下，每个竞技场都提供独特的挑战。在争夺胜利时，利用陷阱和灌木丛获得战略优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/4f64a7435930189907d59f1135283a70.poster.avif?t=1771831372\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/4f64a7435930189907d59f1135283a70.webm?t=1771831372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161450/extras/4f64a7435930189907d59f1135283a70.mp4?t=1771831372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>联手</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友组队进行 2v2 团战。或者，如果您更喜欢单人冒险，可以与人工智能对手测试您的剑刃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>笔记</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过打开或关闭能量提升和友军火力来自定义您的 Blade Blitz 体验。您可以控制竞争的激烈程度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们支持多种控制器，包括 Xbox、PlayStation、Switch 等等。</p>",
